{"type": "article", "id": 24150, "title": "台湾好物", "description": "这本书搭配台北四大街区手绘地图，将生活设计店、传统老店及周边美食搜罗在内。", "date": "2016-03-27T07:55:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11845, "name": "台北"}, {"id": 9626, "name": "小店"}, {"id": 143, "name": "设计"}, {"id": 10636, "name": "旅行指南"}], "category": 5, "column": 29, "author": 18, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 199, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703124329KEBslhxJtNeyCvqT.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>作者简介</h2>\n<p>喜琳，旅行美食撰稿人、旅行博主，曾游走在台北、东京、京都、首尔、曼谷、罗马、佛罗伦萨、维也纳、伊斯坦布尔、柏林、布拉格等地街头，希望用自己的视角，感受和记录每一段不可倒回的旅行。</p>\n<h2>书影实拍</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124328S4b5Jmz7ksL1tjCu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.62666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124328EWSqJActkwYHKRah.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.94210526\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124329wRmiCEz10PAsrY7l.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74798928\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}